# Pending ADR Topics

These should be generated by the ADR agent after the A18 refactoring is complete.

1. ADR-001: Dictionary-based i18n over LinguiJS Macros
   - Context: LinguiJS SWC plugin incompatible with Next.js 15.5
   - Decision: Use custom dictionary system with adapter pattern for future migration
   - Status: Accepted

2. ADR-002: ActionResult<unknown> over specific Prisma types
   - Context: Prisma generated types don't match domain model interfaces
   - Decision: Use unknown generic with as-any casts at call sites
   - Status: Accepted (temporary, until domain models align with Prisma)

3. ADR-003: Self-healing Prisma engines for NixOS
   - Context: NixOS read-only /nix/store + ephemeral /tmp
   - Decision: Auto-download + patchelf in scripts/env.sh
   - Status: Accepted

4. ADR-004: App ↔ Connector ↔ Module (ACL) architecture
   - Context: External APIs crash, change, timeout
   - Decision: Anti-Corruption Layer with resilience per connector
   - Status: Accepted

5. ADR-005: No URL-based locale routing
   - Context: App is auth-gated, no SEO requirement
   - Decision: Locale from user settings/cookie, not URL prefix
   - Status: Accepted

6. ADR-006: || separator for keywords, comma for locations
   - Context: EURES API accepts multiple keywords and location codes
   - Decision: Different separators to avoid ambiguity (commas in job titles)
   - Status: Accepted

7. ADR-007: useTranslations locale override for SSR hydration
   - Context: Server components can't read document.documentElement.lang
   - Decision: Pass locale as prop from server pages to client components
   - Status: Accepted
